{"id": "1281199194404556906", "channel_id": "1281152112214020166", "type": 19, "author_id": "1061602997844586506", "author_name": "nancyjofla", "author_bot": false, "content": "总之感谢建议与喜欢<:ok:1239911197088681994> 感觉能被提出到“风格不统一”就已经算是进步啦23333之后的赛博泥人儿里会多加考虑风格相关的建议不过……嘛，慢慢来吧", "timestamp": "2024-09-05T10:28:11.476000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["676337286769672192"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1281198825100546119", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1281152112214020166", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "（已封存）【蚰蜒的vrm影像馆】", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969"}
